Rewterz Threat Alert Vtflooder Trojan Active IOCs
text: Vtflooder is a trojan infection that can infiltrate your system without your awareness and remain undetected for a long time, despite the suspicious indicators once it settles and activates. After infecting computers, it uses the network connection to upload its payload to an online threat scanning service, most likely to degrade the services speed or stability. This malicious program can infect your computer along with other malware infections and possibly unwanted programs. Vtflooder can collect and steal sensitive data from your computer and create backdoors for further cyber attacks by downloading malicious threats in the devices.
